sourcesContent: import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { MenuItem } from 'primeng/api'; @Component({ selector: 'app-nav-menu', templateUrl: './nav-menu.component.html', styleUrls: ['./nav-menu.component.css'] }) export class NavMenuComponent { isExpanded = false; items: MenuItem[] | undefined; ngOnInit() { this.items = [ { label: 'Home', icon: 'pi-home', url: "/" }, { label: 'Counter', icon: 'pi-plus', url: "/counter" }, { label: 'Fetch Data', icon: 'pi-th-large', url: "/fetch-data" }, { label: 'Google', icon: 'pi-info', url: "https://www.google.com" } ]; } }
